milestones.description: This is the lowest match aggregate (75) involving teams Sri Lanka & Zimbabwe in ODIs
Zimbabwe's 35 is the lowest score in ODIs. They broke the earlier record of 36

stories.title: Zimbabwe hit new lows as Vaas takes 300
stories.subTitle: Zimbabwe v Sri Lanka, 3rd ODI, Harare
stories.summary: The humiliation of the new 'expurgated' Zimbabwe cricket team continued at Harare Sports Club as they crashed to 35 all out, the lowest total ever recorded in a one-day international
